{
  "stem": "7598.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I must say that I never came across anything like that at all.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] My mother had already made inquiries about schools.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was 15 and my brother was 17.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My mother, quite rightly, although I was horrified, threw me into Queens College, where I cried myself to sleep for three months, but I learned English.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The staff were wonderful to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The headmistress helped me with English and the [INAUDIBLE] who herself was-- came out of Germany, was fascinated by my story.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I went to school for Queens College, which seemed to have a lot of daughters of diplomatic service.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were Swedes and Greeks, et cetera, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Strangely enough, I passed my matriculation very well after 15 months and went on to take a high school certificate.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother went to [INAUDIBLE] College.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had always been an outstanding student.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as a child, he wanted to do philosophy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But somehow when he came to England, he felt he wanted to do something more pragmatic and he decided to do medicine.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Although we spent two years together, we really very seldom discussed what happened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was a very introvert child, [SIGHS] basically because he was born, I think, with a birthmark.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And really there was nothing to discuss.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had shared the experience.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's only later on that I would have liked to have talked to him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But he eventually emigrated to America and I didn't see-- I didn't see that much of him until just before he died, when we really started to communicate.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had a recurring dream for years of walking across the channel and never quite making it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In fact, I had this dream for about 20 years or so.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
